
 ImageViewer
=============
    A Small imageviewer based on Qt4


 FEATURES
==========

    *Loads all imageformats Qt has support for
    *Fullscreen viewing(only fullscreen viewing for now actually)
    *Scrolling by Arrowkeys
    *Basic zooming(currently broken...)
    *Imageloading in separate thread
    *Image readahead


 DEPENDENCIES
==============

    Required:
	*Qt 4.2.0 (or higher)


 USAGE
=======

    ImageViewer [OPTION]

        Where [OPTION] is one of the following:
        --image (filename)	Specifies the image you want to load
        --scale			Scales the image to fit the screen
        --version		Prints versionstring


 KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
====================

    PageUp	-	Previous Image
    PageDown	-	Next Image
    0		-	Zoom in
    9		-	Zoom out
    Arrowkeys	-	Scroll around the picture if it is bigger than the screen
    Home	-	Move to first image in imagelist
    End		-	Move to last image in imagelist